data.title: Motion Equity Partners sells Tokheim ProGauge to OPW | Experience
data.meta_description: Jones Day represented Motion Equity Partners LLP in connection with its sale of Tokheim ProGauge, a leading manufacturer and supplier of fuel retailing solutions, to OPW, a subsidiary of Dover Corporation and a global leader in fluid handling, management, monitoring and control solutions for the safe and efficient handling and distribution of fuels and critical fluids.
data.text:
Client(s) Motion Equity Partners LLP

Jones Day represented Motion Equity Partners LLP in connection with its sale of Tokheim ProGauge, a leading manufacturer and supplier of fuel retailing solutions, to OPW, a subsidiary of Dover Corporation and a global leader in fluid handling, management, monitoring and control solutions for the safe and efficient handling and distribution of fuels and critical fluids.
